{"title":"pointer-events","uid":"ba99b041e2cc1b6cb56dc49d495fa921","slug":"pointer-events","date":"2022-07-30T05:01:28.000Z","updated":"2024-10-27T03:02:34.954Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/pointer-events.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/cover1.jpg","content":"<p><code>pointer-events</code>是一个CSS属性，它定义了在何种情况下元素可以成为鼠标事件（或触摸事件）的目标。这个属性可以控制元素是否可以被点击、是否可以触发鼠标事件，或者是否应该忽略鼠标事件，让事件传递给下面的元素。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>pointer-events属性主要用于以下几种场景：</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>None: 元素不会成为鼠标事件的目标。例如，如果想让一个元素透明对用户的点击，可以将其pointer-events设置为none。<br>Auto: 默认值。元素正常响应鼠标事件。</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>移动端h5图片长按可以下载，但想禁用这个默认事件就可以使用此属性</p>\n","text":"pointer-events是一个CSS属性，它定义了在何种情况下元素可以成为鼠标事件（或触摸事件）的目标。这个属性可以控制元素是否可以被点击、是否可以触发鼠标...","permalink":"/post/pointer-events","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":270,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"html&css","slug":"html-css","count":12,"path":"api/categories/html-css.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"css","slug":"css","count":9,"path":"api/tags/css.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"M","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"这是我的博客","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"-webkit-tap-highlight-color","uid":"6bb0ba9791e24ded32fb982c8650bd52","slug":"-webkit-tap-highlight-color","date":"2022-07-31T04:01:36.000Z","updated":"2024-10-27T03:02:49.729Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/-webkit-tap-highlight-color.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/cover1.jpg","text":"iOS禁用点击透明黑色背景 -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent ","permalink":"/post/-webkit-tap-highlight-color","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":55,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"html&css","slug":"html-css","count":12,"path":"api/categories/html-css.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"css","slug":"css","count":9,"path":"api/tags/css.json"}],"author":{"name":"M","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"这是我的博客","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"menu","uid":"f7cd73850062e5beae0d458b739ec82c","slug":"menu","date":"2022-0